{"id":570437,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/10/中文编辑校对网｜今天，各编辑部这样做标题定版/","date":"2017-10-19T07:04:38Z","modified":"2017-10-19T07:04:38Z","title":"中文编辑校对网｜今天，各编辑部这样做标题定版式","content":"<p>常有网友致电中文编辑校对网询问：“怎样才能尽快胜任编辑工作”？我们给出的建议是，从新闻标题制作入手，也许是培养新闻意识，较快进入岗位状态的最佳通道。标题的价值、力量往往可以代表一张报纸。（因各地电子版上线时间不一，本文未列全各地重要报纸）</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/头版.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-570469\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/头版.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"2825\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/头版.jpg 1900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/头版-64x300.jpg 64w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/头版-768x3616.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/新京报.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-570450\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/新京报.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/新京报.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/10/新京报-206x300.jpg 206w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[30303,18804,30319,23589]}